  "remarks": "MOHAMMAD MEHDI NEJAD NOURI was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Persons involved in the nuclear Programme.  Rector of Malek Ashtar University of Defence Technology (chemistry dept, affiliated to MODALF, has conducted experiments on beryllium).\n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
